Temporal improvements noted in life expectancy of patients with colorectal 
cancer; a Dutch population-based study.

Qaderi SM(1), Andersson TML(2), Dickman PW(2), de Wilt JHW(3), Verhoeven RHA(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgical Oncology, Radboud university medical center, Nijmegen, 
